{"tid":1389000,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"九巴司機係連儂牆搞事！","createTime":"2019-07-30T20:10:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T09:15:04.000Z","uid":197691,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"d9a8f6f5c53d29e85887c5d70c4869315b8a347d","tid":1389000,"uid":197691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T20:10:34.000Z","msg":"事發係油尖旺嘅柏景灣站巴士站<br />\n個九巴司機一開始行埋去連儂牆到影相<br />\n點知影影下就發顛掉晒D文具落地下<br />\n咁我就跑埋去問佢做乜事啦<br />\n咁佢又乜都唔答   走返去巴士站到匿埋<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">唔知九巴會點回應呢？</span></span>"},{"pid":"f1b62dae1670d7bebaccbebfd44c936c9e5fded7","tid":1389000,"uid":197691,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T20:12:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ankrCTu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FankrCTu.png&h=8ce9146e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/suc5TrV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fsuc5TrV.png&h=e2e48b49&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7KAWfFk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7KAWfFk.png&h=bacffdd5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/K7RBZ66.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FK7RBZ66.png&h=b2730a33&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5DiMCTR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5DiMCTR.png&h=9f753731&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"632827e7b9fa73a15f4fe6ff70b3e09278bfd295","tid":1389000,"uid":188899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T20:16:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95ab85d56eb0df4dc4db0391f06b2344ef0077c0","tid":1389000,"uid":197691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":